title: The Green Edge
description: All vegan store selling a comprehensive range of groceries, including bulk, chilled food, confectionery and snacks, household products, cosmetics, baby food, environmentally friendly nappies, vegan pet food, books, and planting seeds. Also has fresh cupcakes and brownies, coffee, chai, and cold drinks. Hosts vegan educational and social events. Moved from 3/191 Wardell St, Enoggera.
